## OFFER & VALUE PROP

**What this profile offers:**
AI Sales Agent that replaces a junior sales rep — handles inbound and outbound, knows your product inside and out from day one, ~$3K/month vs $60K-$100K/year for a human rep.

**Unique angle / differentiator:**
Not just an SDR tool — it's a full sales agent that understands your product (pricing, integrations, specs) with no ramp time. Execution capacity that compounds monthly at 1/20th the cost. Built by operators (Chris Lee, Nick Dinsmoor, Paul Fung) who scaled and exited their own B2B services company.

**Talking points:**
- Replaces junior sales rep from day one
- Handles inbound and outbound
- Knows product inside and out with no ramp time
- ~$3K/month vs $60K-$100K/year
- Execution capacity that compounds monthly
- Built by operators who scaled and exited a B2B services company

**Avoid saying:**
Sounding over-personalized

**Free offer / hook:**
None

